title: Terry Moore - Echo #1-8 (Minutemen)
description:
Terry Moore's Echo #1-8 [Ongoing] (Minutemen)

Written and Illustrated by Terry Moore
Published by Abstract Studios since March 2008.

About this series:
Julie Martin is in the wrong place at the wrong time when she finds herself under a strange explosion in the desert sky.
The resulting fallout covers her in a mysterious silver metal that brings her more trouble than she can ever imagine, and a friend to die for.



This compilation includes:

Echo 01 (2008) (Minutemen-Zone).cbr
Echo 02 (2008) (Minutemen-Zone).cbr
Echo 03 (2008) (Minutemen-LockeZone).cbr
Echo 04 (2008) (Minutemen-DangerPowersZone).cbr
Echo 05 (2008) (Minutemen-DTs).cbz
Echo 06 (2008) (Minutemen-DTs).cbz
Echo 07 (2008) (Minutemen-DTs).cbz
Echo 08 (2008) (Minutemen-DTs).cbz


Many thanks to the Minutemen scanners/editors that brought us this series.
